<|startoftext|>To buffer our institutions we need: #ElectoralReform, #JudicialReform, the re-drawing of lines between government and law enforcement, new rules for politics and social media, and on and on. This is something Biden *can* do. But we have to keep him to it.<|endoftext|>
<|startoftext|>What #Biden can do, is buffer our institutions - which took a beating by Trump, but have mostly held up. The US system (we now know) is deeply vulnerable, when the threat comes within the White House, rather than from the outside. This will only get worse in the age of #BigData<|endoftext|>
