<|startoftext|>Can #Biden take us forward? Probably not. More likely it will come from grassroots organizing. In fact, the great silver lining of all this is that democratic engagement was *so* impressive this year .. !!! .. The key is to keep this up between elections, not merely during them.<|endoftext|>
<|startoftext|>The message is a sobering one, because we on the left like to believe in the Manichean myth: that Dems are Good, and Trumpists are Evil. But Democrat complicity with neo-liberalism is unsustainable; as are platforms based on cosmetic rather than structural change.<|endoftext|>
